{"word":"G1861 - ἐπαγγέλλω - epangéllō - ep-ang-el'-lo - Profess","slug":"G1861","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐπαγγέλλω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>epangéllō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ep-ang-el'-lo"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Profess"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03B5;&#x0313;&#x03C0;&#x03B1;&#x03B3;&#x03B3;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03BB;&#x03BB;&#x03C9; - epaggello&#x0304;</b> - <i>ep-ang-el'-lo</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G1909\">G1909</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G32\">G32</a>; to <i>announce upon</i> (reflexively), that is, (by implication) to <i>engage</i> to do something, to <i>assert</i> something respecting oneself: - profess, (make) promise."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1860\">G1860</a>, <a href=\"#/G1862\">G1862</a>, <a href=\"#/G4279\">G4279</a>"}]}